OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPope Francis: The pontiff's
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F'pilgrimage of penance' to 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FCanada                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Pope will make a historic visit    
OL,6, this week to offer a formal apology on 
OL,7, Canadian soil for the harms done by    
OL,8, Catholic-run residential schools across
OL,9, the country.                           
OL,11,FPope Francis, 85, has called the visit 
OL,12,Fa "pilgrimage of penance", and has said
OL,13,Fhe hopes it will help heal the wrongs  
OL,14,Fdone to indigenous people in Canada by 
OL,15,Fthe Roman Catholic Church.             
OL,17,FHis itinerary includes stops in the    
OL,18,Fprovinces of Alberta and Quebec and the
OL,19,Fnorthern territory of Nunavut.         
